title: Autobiography of the Rev. Dr. Alexander Carlyle, Minister of Inveresk,
author: Carlyle, Alexander
snippet: As many people from Inveresk parish frequented  her shop at Dalkeith on market-days, the conversation naturally fell on the subject of who was to be their minister.
